   -- ELECT. COMPONENTS
                                                                                                       

                               2nd Qtr.    2nd Qtr.    %
   6 Firms                      1990        1989      Chg
                                                                                                       

   AMP Inc                     68,299      65,799   +  4
   Grainger (W.W.)             32,090      30,329   +  6
