                         CORPORATE
                                                                                                       

                     One Day This Week
                                                                                                       

   Altera Corp. -- 2.5 million common shares, via
Smith-Barney, Harris Upham &amp; Co.
   Banco Central S.A. -- five million American depository
receipts in U.S. and one million common shares globally, via
Prudential-Bache Capital Funding.
   Cherokee Inc. -- initial four million common shares, via
PaineWebber Inc.
