 -- United States

 -- Denmark
 -- France
 -- Italy
 -- The Netherlands
 -- Spain
 -- West Germany
 -- Ireland
 -- Greece
 -- Portugal
 -- Japan
 -- Belgium*
 -- Luxembourg*
 -- Switzerland*
 (*Recommended)
                                                                                                       

                       Oil Imports Banned
                                                                                                       

 -- Japan
 -- United States
 -- Belgium
 -- Denmark
 -- Britain
 -- France
 -- Italy
 -- West Germany
 -- Ireland
 -- Luxembourg
 -- The Netherlands
 -- Portugal
 -- Spain
 -- Greece
</TEXT>
