   NEW YORK -- The New York Stock Exchange announced two new
listings, while the National Market System of the
over-the-counter stock market added three issues.
   Joining the Big Board is Intellicall Inc., trading under
the symbol ICL. It will begin trading Wednesday. The company,
based in Carrollton, Texas, makes and markets pay telephones.
It previously traded over the counter.
                                                                                                       

